@startuml
!define COMPONENT_COLOR #E1F5FE
!define APP_COLOR #FFF9C4
!define STORAGE_COLOR #F0F4C3
!define DOM_COLOR #FFCCBC

title Solenya Framework - Data Flow Sequence Diagram

actor User
participant "App" as App <<Entry Point>> APP_COLOR
participant "Router" as Router COMPONENT_COLOR
participant "Component" as Component COMPONENT_COLOR
participant "Validator" as Validator COMPONENT_COLOR
participant "Storage" as Storage STORAGE_COLOR
participant "Virtual DOM" as VDOM DOM_COLOR
participant "Browser DOM" as DOM DOM_COLOR
participant "TimeTravel" as TimeTravel COMPONENT_COLOR

== Application Initialization ==
User -> App: Initialize Application
activate App
App -> Storage: Load persisted state
activate Storage
Storage --> App: Return serialized state
deactivate Storage
App -> Component: Create root component
activate Component
Component -> Component: Initialize state
Component --> App: Component instance
App -> VDOM: Create virtual DOM tree
activate VDOM
VDOM --> App: Virtual tree
deactivate VDOM
App -> DOM: Render initial UI
activate DOM
DOM --> User: Display UI
deactivate DOM
deactivate Component
deactivate App

== User Interaction & State Update ==
User -> DOM: Interact (e.g., input, click)
activate DOM
DOM -> Component: Trigger event handler
deactivate DOM
activate Component
Component -> Component: Update internal state
Component -> Validator: Validate input data
activate Validator
Validator -> Validator: Apply validation rules
Validator --> Component: Validation result
deactivate Validator

alt Validation Success
    Component -> Component: Process state change
    Component -> Component: Call update()
    Component -> App: Notify state changed
    activate App
    App -> Storage: Serialize current state
    activate Storage
    Storage -> Storage: Persist to local storage
    Storage --> App: Confirmation
    deactivate Storage
    App -> TimeTravel: Record state snapshot
    activate TimeTravel
    TimeTravel -> TimeTravel: Add to history
    TimeTravel --> App: Snapshot recorded
    deactivate TimeTravel
else Validation Failure
    Component -> Component: Handle validation error
    Component -> User: Display error message
end
deactivate Component

== View Rendering Cycle ==
App -> Component: Trigger render cycle
activate App
activate Component
Component -> Component: Execute view() function
Component -> VDOM: Generate new virtual tree
activate VDOM
VDOM --> Component: New virtual tree
deactivate VDOM
Component --> App: Virtual tree ready
deactivate Component
App -> VDOM: Diff previous and new trees
activate VDOM
VDOM -> VDOM: Calculate patches
VDOM --> App: Patch operations
deactivate VDOM
App -> DOM: Apply patches
activate DOM
DOM -> DOM: Update actual DOM nodes
DOM --> User: Updated UI
deactivate DOM
deactivate App

== Navigation & Routing ==
User -> Router: Navigate to new route
activate Router
Router -> Router: Parse route parameters
Router -> Component: Trigger route change
activate Component
Component -> Component: Update state based on route
Component -> Component: Call update()
Component --> Router: State updated
deactivate Component
Router -> App: Request re-render
activate App
App -> VDOM: Create virtual tree for new route
activate VDOM
VDOM --> App: Virtual tree
deactivate VDOM
App -> DOM: Render new view
activate DOM
DOM --> User: Display new page
deactivate DOM
deactivate App
deactivate Router

== Parent-Child Component Communication ==
Component -> Component: Create child component
activate Component
Component -> Component: Pass props to child
activate Component #DarkSalmon
Component -> Component: Child initializes state
Component -> Component: Child calls view()
Component --> Component: Child virtual tree
deactivate Component
Component -> Component: Embed child in parent view
Component -> App: Notify update complete
activate App
App -> Component: Trigger updated event
Component -> Component: Observe child changes
Component -> Component: React to child state
deactivate App
deactivate Component

== Time Travel Debugging ==
User -> TimeTravel: Request previous state
activate TimeTravel
TimeTravel -> TimeTravel: Retrieve snapshot from history
TimeTravel -> App: Restore previous state
activate App
App -> Component: Deserialize state
activate Component
Component -> Component: Restore component state
Component --> App: State restored
deactivate Component
App -> VDOM: Generate virtual tree
activate VDOM
VDOM --> App: Virtual tree
deactivate VDOM
App -> DOM: Render historical state
activate DOM
DOM --> User: Display previous UI state
deactivate DOM
deactivate App
deactivate TimeTravel

== Hot Module Reloading ==
User -> App: Trigger hot reload
activate App
App -> Storage: Serialize current state
activate Storage
Storage --> App: State serialized
deactivate Storage
App -> App: Reload module
App -> Component: Recreate components
activate Component
Component -> Component: Initialize with preserved state
Component --> App: Components ready
deactivate Component
App -> VDOM: Generate virtual tree
activate VDOM
VDOM --> App: Virtual tree
deactivate VDOM
App -> DOM: Re-render
activate DOM
DOM --> User: Updated UI (state preserved)
deactivate DOM
deactivate App

== Asynchronous Operation ==
Component -> Component: Trigger async operation
activate Component
Component -> Component: Call async function
activate Component #LightBlue
Component -> Component: Await external data
Component -> Component: Receive data
Component -> Component: Update state
Component -> Component: Call update()
deactivate Component
Component -> App: Notify state changed
activate App
App -> VDOM: Re-render cycle
activate VDOM
VDOM --> App: Virtual tree
deactivate VDOM
App -> DOM: Update UI
activate DOM
DOM --> User: Display updated data
deactivate DOM
deactivate App
deactivate Component

@enduml
